-- Bollore Invests More Than $30 Million in Freetown Cargo Terminal
-- B y   S i l a s   G b a n d i a
-- 2012-07-03T16:56:08Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-07-03/bollore-invests-more-than-30-million-in-freetown-cargo-terminal.html
Bollore (BOL)  SA’s African unit invested
more than $30 million in about 13 months at the container
terminal in  Sierra Leone ’s capital, Freetown, Eric Melet,
managing director of the company’s African logistics division,
said in an interview today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Silas Gbandia in Freetown at 
